1
00:02:13,960 --> 00:02:16,000
This is the story of :
"Mr. Sharma and Mr. Verma"

2
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:19,560
One is smart while the other is stupid

3
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:22,360
"Mr. Sharma is careful."

4
00:02:22,440 --> 00:02:24,640
"Mr. Verma falls in
trouble every now and then."

5
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:28,360
"Mr. Sharma does long term planning."

6
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:32,480
"Mr. Verma does not
think of too far ahead."

7
00:02:32,560 --> 00:02:34,840
"So what do you think,
who do you want to be?"

8
00:02:34,920 --> 00:02:37,240
"Mr. Sharma or Mr. Verma?"

9
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:38,720
"Think now, act now."

10
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:43,080
"Invest in smart savings
plan and secure your future."

11
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:44,920
"Be a Sharma."

12
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:47,880
I don't know.

13
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:50,280
Something is missing in this ad.

14
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,960
We will finalize the logo by tomorrow.

15
00:02:54,040 --> 00:02:55,240
Is it the color..
- I don't know.

16
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:57,160
I can't put my finger on it.
- Okay.

17
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:02,040
Is it the.. design.. - Anyway,
let me think about it on my flight.

18
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:03,200
And I will let you
know when I get to Delhi.

19
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:05,880
But Vineet please, we need
this perfect by this week.

20
00:03:06,040 --> 00:03:07,880
We are already
running behind schedule.

21
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:10,280
I want it absolutely right, okay?
- Yes, ma'am.

22
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,920
Okay.

23
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,040
Thank you.
- We will get back to you.

24
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,200
Hello Zenobia

25
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,720
Nice of you to join us so early.

26
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,920
Sorry, ma'am..
- I know, lots of traffic, right?

27
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,760
Here's your flight ticket to Delhi.

28
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:55,800
And this is for Los Angeles on Monday.

29
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,560
Change this flight to Sunday.

30
00:03:59,600 --> 00:04:00,680
I need some more time

31
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:01,840
Yes ma'am.

32
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:04,240
Aren't you getting late?
- For what?

33
00:04:04,480 --> 00:04:05,560
Your flight to Delhi.

34
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:07,720
Its at 4:30, right?

35
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,840
Okay, tell Varun that I will finish..

36
00:04:09,920 --> 00:04:12,040
..this report on the flight
and send it back to him. - Okay.

37
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:14,760
Cc Mr. Mehra on the third
stage of the Hot-ends deal.

38
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,120
And please ask FedEx..

39
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:17,520
..about the status on my roeters.

40
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:21,400
Tell Niharika, that its sea
green and not marine blue.

41
00:04:21,840 --> 00:04:22,920
Okay.

42
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:24,320
Call Vineet from Trikaya.

43
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,840
Actually, forget it.
I will do it myself.

44
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:29,960
Ask my driver to bring the
car to the porch. - Yes, ma'am.

45
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,160
Lower the volume

46
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:38,960
Yes.

47
00:04:39,760 --> 00:04:40,840
Yes, on the way.

48
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,160
Airport.

49
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:47,240
We'll have to cancel the party.

50
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:50,920
No, I have to go to LA on Sunday.

51
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:52,960
Yes, it's preponed.

52
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:57,160
Yes, you also know how it is.

53
00:04:58,360 --> 00:05:00,240
Okay, we'll talk about
it when we meet. Okay.

54
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:01,640
Okay, see you.

55
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:05,800
Love you. Bye.

56
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:21,320
Aunty, aunty, give me Rs.2.

57
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:23,400
I want to eat something.
I'll eat some food.

58
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,880
Please, aunty.

59
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:27,000
Aunty, what's that on the television?

60
00:05:28,960 --> 00:05:30,360
Aunty, what's that on the television?

61
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:32,400
Look, remember we saw it back there..

62
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,680
..it is on the TV now.

63
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:37,960
Sweetheart, may you
get a handsome husband

64
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,200
Give us some money, come on!

65
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:40,760
Give it.

66
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:43,040
Cheapskate.

67
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:56,040
Blow the horn.

68
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:01,200
Oh, my! I don't believe this.

69
00:06:01,480 --> 00:06:03,320
These are the worst kind of people.

70
00:06:20,200 --> 00:06:21,240
Sorry.

71
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,960
Come on.

72
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,080
Let's go, let's go.

73
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,720
What the..

74
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:40,000
Constable.
- What is it?

75
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:42,080
What is the problem? The traffic
is jammed from both the ends.

76
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:44,480
Madam, the traffic jam
is going to get worse.

77
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:46,720
A huge rally is going to pass by.
- Rally?

78
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,920
Yes.
- But I am getting late.

79
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:51,240
I am sorry, madam, but everyone
will have to take a diversion.

80
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:52,400
Okay.
- What?

81
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:54,160
Everyone! Take the lane to your left.

82
00:06:55,960 --> 00:06:57,160
Great.

83
00:06:58,240 --> 00:07:00,720
'Welcome to Chhatrapati
Shivaji Airport..' - Your ID, please.

84
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,520
Sorry.

85
00:07:02,840 --> 00:07:04,400
Excuse me, please. Sorry.

86
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:06,040
Ma'am, please. Do you mind?

87
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:08,720
Please. Please.
- Are we standing in the line for fun?

88
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:11,520
Flight to Delhi.
- Ma'am, you have missed your flight.

89
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:12,720
That's not possible, check it.

90
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:14,200
Sorry, ma'am, but
the gates are closed.

91
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:15,400
I can't help you.

92
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,560
You are late.

93
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:18,160
What do you mean by I am late?

94
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:20,560
Sorry, ma'am, airline rules.

95
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:23,040
Airline rules!

96
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:25,720
Do you know how much
business I give your airline?

97
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:28,720
Me alone!
- I really can't help you, please.

98
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:33,640
When is the next flight?
- 11 o'clock at night.

99
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:34,840
What?

100
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:37,480
Listen, I need to go right now.

101
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,520
Aren't there any flights before that?

102
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,840
Not before 11 o'clock.

103
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:43,720
Only if you want to
travel by any budget airlines.

104
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:47,480
Budget airlines.

105
00:07:50,160 --> 00:07:51,600
One outlook money please

106
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:53,800
Rs.30, madam.

107
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:58,840
No change, madam.

108
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:00,680
You must have. Check again

109
00:08:01,280 --> 00:08:02,800
I really don't have change ma'am

110
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:13,600
How much?
- For 1000.

111
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:15,720
Just a minute.

112
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,480
Here is your change, ma'am.

113
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:50,400
You are welcome.

114
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:58,040
25.

115
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:00,960
Do you want a different magazine?

116
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:05,240
Will they get married?

117
00:09:05,320 --> 00:09:06,480
What do you think?

118
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,760
Saif-Kareena.

119
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:10,600
How would I know

120
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:13,600
Well, If we don't know..
Why waste money on this magazine?

121
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,760
Sir, you should have
checked-in the bags.

122
00:09:31,560 --> 00:09:33,280
But why, they're not that large!

123
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:35,200
And check-in or cabin, finally
all are going to reach Delhi.

124
00:09:35,280 --> 00:09:37,480
What's the big deal. Relax.

125
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:42,360
Yes, hello.

126
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:45,800
I have already boarded.

127
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:50,200
No, keep talking.

128
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:53,280
I am only traveling by
the plane, not flying it.

129
00:09:55,400 --> 00:09:56,520
Yes.

130
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:01,080
What?

131
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:03,200
I said 15 and not 12.

132
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:05,120
How much? Yes.

133
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:09,120
Tell that boy we are
here to do business..

134
00:10:09,160 --> 00:10:10,320
..and not to waste time.

135
00:10:10,400 --> 00:10:12,320
And we are not scared of him.

136
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:14,560
Tell him that's the final rate.

137
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:17,120
And also add that 'no
room for discussion' clause.

138
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:18,560
Yes.

139
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:22,040
Useless.

140
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:25,200
These Mumbaikars think
we Delhilites are fools.

141
00:10:28,760 --> 00:10:31,360
So? Delhi?
- Delhi.

142
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,600
"..and pay attention to us."

143
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:34,280
"During the flight you.."

144
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:36,560
That's a nice shirt. Is it readymade?

145
00:10:37,240 --> 00:10:39,000
Must be. Who gets
clothes tailored nowadays?

146
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:41,760
'Fasten your seat belts.'

147
00:10:41,800 --> 00:10:43,440
'And follow our instructions.'

148
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:44,760
Forget it.

149
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:46,640
When our lives are in danger..

150
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,720
..she will be the first one
to jump out with her tray.

151
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:50,960
And we'll be searching for
the front door, middle door..

152
00:10:51,080 --> 00:10:54,840
..and back door and
reach the heaven's door

153
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:58,360
Heaven's door. Front door.. Get it?

154
00:10:58,440 --> 00:11:00,680
'It will come down from the
panel above..' - That's okay.

155
00:11:00,760 --> 00:11:02,240
'..and the effect of oxygen..'

156
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:04,360
Have you ever tried the oxygen mask?

157
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:05,920
Gives a nice high.

158
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,720
The mind feels light.

159
00:11:08,040 --> 00:11:09,320
Try it sometime.

160
00:11:15,720 --> 00:11:17,960
So I explained to my wife,
"What are you so concerned about?"

161
00:11:18,040 --> 00:11:19,760
"You mind your own business."

162
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:22,800
"As far as uncle is concerned,
there is nothing to worry about."

163
00:11:22,880 --> 00:11:24,760
"We will lay a mattress on the
terrace next to the parapet."

164
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:26,800
Where?
- Parapet

165
00:11:26,880 --> 00:11:28,600
No, on the terrace.

166
00:11:28,760 --> 00:11:29,960
Do you want to get uncle killed..

167
00:11:30,040 --> 00:11:31,640
..by hanging him from
the 30 feet high parapet?

168
00:11:32,800 --> 00:11:34,280
You aren't paying attention

169
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:37,760
What do you do? You're in a
job or run your own business?

170
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:42,560
I am at.. the IIT..
- so you're still studying.

171
00:11:42,920 --> 00:11:44,800
That's why you're
not paying attention.

172
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:56,240
Passengers are requested not
to open their seat-belts..

173
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:58,560
.. and stay at their seats..

174
00:11:58,600 --> 00:12:00,520
..till the plane comes to a
complete halt. - Hold this.

175
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:01,880
See you.

176
00:12:02,720 --> 00:12:05,840
Yes, hello.
- Excuse me, sir, please be seated.

177
00:12:05,920 --> 00:12:08,440
What's the big deal.

178
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:10,560
We've landed after all.
- Yes, Hello.

179
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:12,960
I have just landed. Where are you?

180
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:15,760
'Flight IT8..'

181
00:12:15,840 --> 00:12:18,840
Vikram, I can't go on Monday.

182
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:21,680
But if it's my birthday and
I don't want to do anything..

183
00:12:21,760 --> 00:12:23,400
..then I just don't
seem to understand..

184
00:12:24,520 --> 00:12:26,960
Listen, hold on.
That's my bag. I'll call you.

185
00:12:33,640 --> 00:12:34,760
Okay, I have got my bag.

186
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:36,240
Yes, I am coming out.

187
00:12:37,520 --> 00:12:39,040
The battery is very low

188
00:12:39,600 --> 00:12:40,680
I will see you there.

189
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:58,200
Yes, I am coming out. At exit no..

190
00:12:58,280 --> 00:13:00,880
Welcome to Jaipur
International airport.

191
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:03,360
Welcome to Jaipur
International airport.

192
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:05,160
I am in Jaipur!

193
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:07,440
Vikram, I am in Jaipur!

194
00:13:08,240 --> 00:13:09,640
I don't know, let me call you back.

195
00:13:16,280 --> 00:13:18,360
I realized after
I landed at the airport here.

196
00:13:19,320 --> 00:13:21,200
I don't know, there's some
major technical problem..

197
00:13:21,280 --> 00:13:22,720
..or something like that,
at the Delhi airport.

198
00:13:22,800 --> 00:13:24,480
All the flights are landing in Jaipur.

199
00:13:24,560 --> 00:13:25,680
It's freezing here.

200
00:13:25,800 --> 00:13:26,920
They did make the announcement..

201
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,280
..but I was asleep on the flight.

202
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:29,760
Hang on a minute.

203
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:34,680
It's freezing.

204
00:13:42,440 --> 00:13:43,960
Listen, don't worry.

205
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:45,960
I will hire a car and come to Delhi.

206
00:13:47,160 --> 00:13:48,640
Because there is no
other choice, Vikram.

207
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:50,520
There are no other
flights till morning.

208
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:53,520
Vikram, don't get
over-protective on me now.

209
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:54,760
I can't handle it.

210
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:57,200
I am hanging up now.
My battery is down.

211
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:58,360
Okay.

212
00:14:01,800 --> 00:14:02,960
What happened?

213
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:05,160
Madam, the machine has broken down.

214
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:06,520
The card isn't working.

215
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:07,760
You will have to pay cash.

216
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,800
The plane is not working.

217
00:14:09,880 --> 00:14:11,240
Your machine isn't working.

218
00:14:11,640 --> 00:14:13,040
Is everyone's mind working?

219
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:14,440
That's working properly.

220
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:16,600
How much?
- 4000.

221
00:14:23,320 --> 00:14:24,400
Here.

222
00:14:24,640 --> 00:14:26,080
This is three..
- Wait.

223
00:14:31,800 --> 00:14:32,880
Will do.

224
00:14:36,560 --> 00:14:38,920
Here, the receipt to your car.
- Thank you.

225
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:41,720
You will find it in the parking
lot behind the second gate. Yes.

226
00:14:41,800 --> 00:14:44,240
Okay.
- Madam. Greetings.

227
00:14:44,400 --> 00:14:45,480
Welcome to my land.

228
00:14:46,160 --> 00:14:47,600
Like there was a choice!

229
00:14:48,200 --> 00:14:49,280
See you.

230
00:15:43,400 --> 00:15:44,520
Excuse me.

231
00:15:54,760 --> 00:15:55,800
I have to go to Delhi.

232
00:16:09,320 --> 00:16:11,360
How long will it take to reach Delhi?

233
00:16:13,120 --> 00:16:15,160
Six hours.
- What?

234
00:16:15,920 --> 00:16:17,200
Six hours.

235
00:16:19,760 --> 00:16:21,160
And if you drive faster?

236
00:16:22,040 --> 00:16:23,720
This is my speed.

237
00:16:24,520 --> 00:16:27,600
For the past 11 years.
- Very good.

238
00:16:33,680 --> 00:16:35,040
Hey, what are you doing?

239
00:16:37,720 --> 00:16:40,360
I haven't slept for
the past 32 hours, madam.

240
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:43,160
I have been driving non-stop.

241
00:16:44,080 --> 00:16:46,560
What choices do the poor have?

242
00:16:47,240 --> 00:16:50,320
Just keep toiling hard all day long.

243
00:16:50,520 --> 00:16:53,120
Look, will you be
able to drive safely?

244
00:16:53,200 --> 00:16:54,400
Or should I hire another car?

245
00:17:00,160 --> 00:17:02,920
Hire another car.
- What?

246
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:04,160
Are you crazy?

247
00:17:04,880 --> 00:17:06,000
You cannot do that.

248
00:17:06,280 --> 00:17:08,000
You hire another car..

249
00:17:08,080 --> 00:17:10,000
..and I will take another fare.

250
00:17:10,080 --> 00:17:11,600
Where would you like to go, mister?

251
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:13,400
How dare you speak to me like this!

252
00:17:13,480 --> 00:17:15,400
Look, I will file
a complain against you, okay?

253
00:17:15,640 --> 00:17:16,920
Start the car.

254
00:17:16,960 --> 00:17:18,080
You took the money, didn't you?

255
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:20,440
So do I owe you my life!

256
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:28,160
Madam, its you! Are you okay?
- What okay?

257
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:30,000
I hired this car to go to Delhi.

258
00:17:30,080 --> 00:17:31,240
And now he's saying he won't go.

259
00:17:31,320 --> 00:17:32,400
He's saying, "Hire another car".

260
00:17:33,160 --> 00:17:34,520
You said so yourself.

261
00:17:35,520 --> 00:17:36,760
Sir, where do you want to go?

262
00:17:36,840 --> 00:17:38,200
Are you drunk?

263
00:17:38,960 --> 00:17:40,040
Come here.

264
00:17:41,400 --> 00:17:42,760
Why don't you take her?

265
00:17:42,840 --> 00:17:44,240
You can't force me to.

266
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:46,600
It's my car.
I decide who I want to take

267
00:17:46,880 --> 00:17:47,960
Or not take.

268
00:17:48,040 --> 00:17:51,000
It sure is your car,
but I've hired it.

269
00:17:51,080 --> 00:17:53,160
You talk as if you've bought it.

270
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:56,200
One call can make you rot in jail.

271
00:17:56,280 --> 00:17:58,120
Don't you know how to talk to a lady?

272
00:17:58,360 --> 00:17:59,400
Go ahead.

273
00:17:59,920 --> 00:18:01,000
You too slap me.

274
00:18:01,240 --> 00:18:04,080
The entire world can do
whatever they want with the poor.

275
00:18:04,160 --> 00:18:06,760
I will crush your jaw
with a single punch.

276
00:18:06,840 --> 00:18:08,280
Then you can drive your car in
the reverse gear all your life.

277
00:18:08,800 --> 00:18:10,480
No, please, don't.. don't argue.

278
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:13,800
Don't worry, I know how
to deal with such rascals.

279
00:18:13,880 --> 00:18:15,360
Why won't you go? Start the car.

280
00:18:15,440 --> 00:18:16,640
I will come along as well.

281
00:18:17,040 --> 00:18:18,160
Don't worry.

282
00:18:23,080 --> 00:18:24,400
Let's go. Delhi.

283
00:18:24,720 --> 00:18:26,760
Don't worry, I am coming along.

284
00:18:27,400 --> 00:18:29,280
Come on. Now just drive the car.

285
00:18:29,320 --> 00:18:31,240
And don't even dare to stop the car..

286
00:18:31,320 --> 00:18:32,800
..or your breathing
till we reach Delhi.

287
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:36,880
But.. - Actually the Roadways'
bus is running late by two hours.

288
00:18:37,760 --> 00:18:40,320
So I thought he will stay in control..

289
00:18:40,400 --> 00:18:41,880
..if there's a man with you.

290
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:43,760
But you'll have to pay extra fare.

291
00:18:43,840 --> 00:18:45,680
There you go again!

292
00:18:45,760 --> 00:18:47,040
Should I remove my belt?

293
00:18:49,280 --> 00:18:52,800
You.. you can just drop
me on the way. - Where?

294
00:18:52,880 --> 00:18:56,200
There.. on the way,
near Chandni Chowk. - What?

295
00:19:01,800 --> 00:19:03,240
Are you from Delhi?

296
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:08,680
Are you from Delhi?

297
00:19:09,240 --> 00:19:10,320
No.

298
00:19:11,640 --> 00:19:12,840
Why?

299
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:14,760
Does everyone traveling to
Delhi have to be from there?

300
00:19:14,840 --> 00:19:15,920
You're right.

301
00:19:15,960 --> 00:19:17,680
He could be from Kashmir as well.

302
00:19:18,880 --> 00:19:20,960
My husband is.
- From Kashmir?

303
00:19:22,240 --> 00:19:23,840
Delhi.
- I see. Delhi.

304
00:19:23,920 --> 00:19:25,480
Where in Delhi?

305
00:19:26,440 --> 00:19:28,840
Chanakyapuri.
- Chanakyapuri.

306
00:19:28,920 --> 00:19:31,160
Where in Chanakyapuri?

307
00:19:34,200 --> 00:19:37,440
Ninth main.
- Ninth main.

308
00:19:37,480 --> 00:19:39,400
Where in Ninth main?

309
00:19:40,040 --> 00:19:42,720
Bungalow no. 44, have you been there?

310
00:19:43,480 --> 00:19:47,720
Bungalow no. 44, Ninth main,
Chanakyapuri, Delhi. No.

311
00:19:47,800 --> 00:19:49,480
I have never been there.

312
00:19:51,760 --> 00:19:53,720
Do you want to get us
killed at this young age?

313
00:19:53,800 --> 00:19:55,040
Open your eyes. He was dozing off.

314
00:19:55,120 --> 00:19:57,080
Stop the car. Stop the car.

315
00:19:58,200 --> 00:20:02,040
Don't worry, I have travelled
between Delhi and Jaipur many a times.

316
00:20:02,120 --> 00:20:04,960
I can drive on this
road with my eyes shut.

317
00:20:05,480 --> 00:20:07,720
Even he was driving
with his eyes shut.

318
00:20:09,720 --> 00:20:11,720
Sit properly.

319
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:14,080
You get worried very easily.

320
00:20:14,160 --> 00:20:17,000
It's not your fault.

321
00:20:17,080 --> 00:20:19,320
Those who belong to New Delhi
are the nervous sorts.

322
00:20:19,400 --> 00:20:21,200
I am from Old Delhi myself.

323
00:20:21,280 --> 00:20:23,000
You must have heard of Chandni Chowk.

324
00:20:23,080 --> 00:20:25,640
The 'Gurdwara' (Sikh Temple)
there is very famous.

325
00:20:25,720 --> 00:20:26,880
That's where my home is.

326
00:20:26,960 --> 00:20:29,200
But I work in Karol Baug.

327
00:20:29,280 --> 00:20:30,520
It takes me 11 minutes everyday..

328
00:20:30,600 --> 00:20:32,680
..to reach Karol Baug on my scooter.

329
00:20:32,760 --> 00:20:34,120
I have my own shop.

330
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,920
Ladies' dress material and saris.

331
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:40,320
I mean American silk, Indian silk,
Dhaka Silk, georgette..

332
00:20:40,400 --> 00:20:42,040
..poplin, you name it!

333
00:20:42,120 --> 00:20:44,040
Retail and wholesale. Both.

334
00:20:44,120 --> 00:20:48,440
It's in the alley in front
of Nathuram Confectioners.

335
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:50,120
Incase you want to drop by someday

336
00:20:50,200 --> 00:20:52,440
Which alley?
- Nathuram Confectioners.

337
00:20:52,520 --> 00:20:55,800
No, the alley in front of it..
- Please look ahead and drive.

338
00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:58,560
Only if this guy lets me.

339
00:20:58,640 --> 00:21:00,480
Sit properly.

340
00:21:01,520 --> 00:21:06,400
Madam, I was wondering..
if you don't mind..

341
00:21:14,840 --> 00:21:17,320
What do you do?

342
00:21:18,360 --> 00:21:19,560
I'm into banking.

343
00:21:19,640 --> 00:21:23,960
Bank. Which bank?
- What do you mean?

344
00:21:24,040 --> 00:21:25,840
I mean the bank that you work in..

345
00:21:25,920 --> 00:21:27,840
..which bank is it?

346
00:21:28,520 --> 00:21:31,400
It's not like you think.
It's investment banking.

347
00:21:31,480 --> 00:21:32,880
Securities.
- I see. I get it.

348
00:21:32,960 --> 00:21:36,760
You must be posted in
the head office branch.

349
00:21:36,840 --> 00:21:38,680
No.

350
00:21:39,080 --> 00:21:41,280
You know what? Forget it.

351
00:21:42,960 --> 00:21:44,800
I get it.

352
00:21:45,640 --> 00:21:46,720
You must be thinking..

353
00:21:46,800 --> 00:21:48,400
..that how can this
man from Chandni Chowk..

354
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:51,920
..understand about banking?
- I don't mean it like that.

355
00:21:52,000 --> 00:21:53,360
No, no, it's okay.

356
00:21:53,440 --> 00:21:57,200
By the way, madam,
I am not like I seem to be.

357
00:21:57,280 --> 00:21:59,640
I am more cunning than a 'Lomdi'.

358
00:22:00,040 --> 00:22:03,680
'Lomdi'. Wolf.
- Fox.

359
00:22:04,040 --> 00:22:07,120
Fox, wolf, same family.
They are cousins.

360
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:09,280
Its okay if you don't want to tell me.

361
00:22:09,360 --> 00:22:14,120
If that's so, then let me tell
you in detail what I do. - Okay.

362
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:17,320
Basically, we help in the capital
formation of businesses.

363
00:22:17,400 --> 00:22:19,880
By the way of outright
purchase or security sales..

364
00:22:19,960 --> 00:22:21,880
..which the issuer offers.

365
00:22:21,960 --> 00:22:25,000
We do this through
standby or separate selling..

366
00:22:25,080 --> 00:22:28,480
..to the US market
specializing in dollar investments.

367
00:22:29,040 --> 00:22:31,440
Got it.
- I got it.

368
00:22:31,760 --> 00:22:34,520
It means our professions are similar.

369
00:22:34,600 --> 00:22:36,360
Investment banking and poplin?

370
00:22:36,440 --> 00:22:38,640
Look, you sell American dollars..

371
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:40,960
..and I sell American georgette.

372
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:44,320
Isn't it?
- Now I have heard it all.

373
00:22:48,400 --> 00:22:50,240
Music.

374
00:22:50,320 --> 00:22:52,200
Which music do you listen to?

375
00:22:52,520 --> 00:22:55,040
I know, you must
listen to English music.

376
00:22:55,120 --> 00:22:57,240
I can say that just looking at you.

377
00:22:58,520 --> 00:23:02,920
"Moments alive just passing you by"

378
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:06,880
"And you know that its cupid's time"

379
00:23:06,960 --> 00:23:09,840
"Because its never coming back"

380
00:23:09,920 --> 00:23:14,560
"Just gone a flight"

381
00:23:15,680 --> 00:23:21,040
"Last time is beating,
time is beating, time is beating."

382
00:23:21,120 --> 00:23:22,720
How far have we reached?

383
00:23:23,560 --> 00:23:24,760
You woke up.

384
00:23:24,840 --> 00:23:27,320
Seems like you are used to
falling asleep on journeys.

385
00:23:27,400 --> 00:23:30,640
Where are we?
- Actually we just crossed Shahpura.

386
00:23:30,720 --> 00:23:31,920
We'll soon be reaching Behrol.

387
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:34,720
Then Dharuvera then Gurgaon.

388
00:23:34,800 --> 00:23:36,680
Shahpura?

389
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:41,240
We are headed to Ajmer!
- Ajmer.

390
00:23:41,320 --> 00:23:43,440
No chance! Why would we go to Ajmer?

391
00:23:43,520 --> 00:23:46,360
Please ask someone.
- Don't worry.

392
00:23:46,440 --> 00:23:48,440
Just relax and sit comfortably.

393
00:23:48,520 --> 00:23:50,720
Two hours later you will be
comfortably sitting on your bed..

394
00:23:50,800 --> 00:23:52,560
..and watching television.

395
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:57,960
But why haven't we
crossed the Behrol bridge yet?

396
00:23:58,040 --> 00:24:01,640
And where did this
rough patch come from

397
00:24:02,200 --> 00:24:06,920
It says Mumbai 950 kilometers.
Where are we going?

398
00:24:06,960 --> 00:24:09,760
You are driving
in the opposite direction. - No chance.

399
00:24:09,840 --> 00:24:11,160
Why would I drive in
the opposite direction?

400
00:24:11,240 --> 00:24:14,160
I took a diversion 10 kilometers back.

401
00:24:14,240 --> 00:24:17,680
I took a big u-turn and
then two small u-turns.

402
00:24:20,640 --> 00:24:22,280
You are heading in the
opposite direction. - By God!

403
00:24:22,360 --> 00:24:24,520
They've changed all the
roads in the past two years.

404
00:24:24,600 --> 00:24:25,640
Mark my words..

405
00:24:25,720 --> 00:24:28,040
..this government won't
last for long. - Be quiet.

406
00:24:28,120 --> 00:24:29,320
Just shut up.

407
00:24:29,360 --> 00:24:31,240
Excuse me. Hey, you.

408
00:24:31,280 --> 00:24:32,760
Driver.

409
00:24:32,840 --> 00:24:34,720
What is his name?

410
00:24:38,240 --> 00:24:40,040
Shivrattan

411
00:24:40,600 --> 00:24:42,040
Wake him up.

412
00:24:42,120 --> 00:24:44,920
Hey, get up.
Madam is asking something.

413
00:24:45,200 --> 00:24:48,480
Oh honey! why are you getting annoyed?

414
00:24:48,520 --> 00:24:51,360
What happened?
- What are you blabbering? Wake up.

415
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:52,760
This man is taking us
somewhere else all together!

416
00:24:52,840 --> 00:24:54,960
Where am I taking you? All
of us are going to Delhi.

417
00:24:55,040 --> 00:24:56,440
You just stop the car. Stop it.

418
00:24:56,520 --> 00:24:59,520
What's the big deal.

419
00:25:04,520 --> 00:25:07,880
Where are we? - Just a minute,
madam. I will find out.

420
00:25:07,960 --> 00:25:09,160
God!

421
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:12,760
This is the worst
car I've traveled in.

422
00:25:29,120 --> 00:25:31,080
What is he doing?

423
00:25:39,760 --> 00:25:41,080
Is he serious?

424
00:25:41,160 --> 00:25:43,560
Seems like he used to
drive a steamroller before.

425
00:25:43,640 --> 00:25:45,880
You be quiet!

426
00:25:45,960 --> 00:25:48,800
What? Where are we?
- I don't know, madam.

427
00:25:52,200 --> 00:25:55,120
He said, "I have been
driving for 11 years".

428
00:25:55,920 --> 00:25:58,480
So? You have been driving for
the past 11 years, haven't you?

429
00:25:58,560 --> 00:26:01,320
I used to drive on the
Shimla-Manali road, madam.

430
00:26:01,960 --> 00:26:03,200
Why am I not surprised?

431
00:26:03,280 --> 00:26:04,840
Why are you asking this fool?

432
00:26:04,920 --> 00:26:06,560
He was sniffing the road.

433
00:26:06,640 --> 00:26:08,120
Get in the car

434
00:26:08,200 --> 00:26:10,600
Don't worry, madam.

435
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:13,480
We've only lost our way, that's all.

436
00:26:13,560 --> 00:26:15,840
What's the big deal.

437
00:26:20,840 --> 00:26:22,960
It will start right now.

438
00:26:34,600 --> 00:26:36,920
Yes, hello? Vikram, I..

439
00:26:36,960 --> 00:26:38,360
What?

440
00:26:38,440 --> 00:26:42,000
No. Not now.

441
00:26:42,080 --> 00:26:43,720
God, I can't believe this.

442
00:26:43,760 --> 00:26:45,480
What happened?

443
00:26:45,560 --> 00:26:47,000
The battery is dead.

444
00:26:47,080 --> 00:26:50,200
So what's the big deal! Use my phone.

445
00:26:50,960 --> 00:26:52,800
Take it.

446
00:26:52,880 --> 00:26:54,640
Talk. Go on.

447
00:26:56,560 --> 00:26:58,440
I will go take a look.

448
00:26:58,840 --> 00:27:02,440
Bablu, I suggest that
you check the carburetor.

449
00:27:02,520 --> 00:27:04,200
That's where the problem always is.

450
00:27:04,280 --> 00:27:07,440
Your theory would have
been helpful in the 1980s

451
00:27:07,520 --> 00:27:10,640
A car with fuel-injection
system doesn't have a carburetor.

452
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:12,880
It doesn't!

453
00:27:13,400 --> 00:27:15,040
That's why it broke down.

454
00:27:15,120 --> 00:27:17,320
Our car broke down.

455
00:27:18,840 --> 00:27:21,200
Vikram, don't get hyper.

456
00:27:21,680 --> 00:27:23,640
No, I will be there. You stay put.

457
00:27:23,720 --> 00:27:26,360
I'll call my friend.

458
00:27:26,440 --> 00:27:28,840
He will come and fix it.

459
00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:31,480
He is a mechanic.
- When will he come?

460
00:27:31,560 --> 00:27:34,800
He will be here in 1-11/2 hour.

461
00:27:35,640 --> 00:27:37,400
Want some?

462
00:27:37,480 --> 00:27:39,520
I just called to tell you that..

463
00:27:39,600 --> 00:27:41,640
..it can take a little longer, okay?

464
00:27:41,720 --> 00:27:44,080
Just relax, we are fixing it.

465
00:27:44,320 --> 00:27:46,760
Okay, I am hanging up. See you. Bye.

466
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:51,280
Thank you.
- Welcome.

467
00:27:51,800 --> 00:27:53,880
Is it fixed? - very soon.
I showed the fool how to do it.

468
00:27:53,960 --> 00:27:56,160
Don't worry, here, take a bite.

469
00:27:56,240 --> 00:27:58,440
This snack clubbed with red
chilly pickle is my specialty.

470
00:27:58,520 --> 00:27:59,680
Ready to eat in two seconds.

471
00:27:59,760 --> 00:28:01,560
Noodles still take
two minutes to prepare.

472
00:28:01,640 --> 00:28:02,680
I am not hungry.

473
00:28:02,760 --> 00:28:04,600
How much longer will it take?

474
00:28:04,840 --> 00:28:07,720
Around 1-11/2 hour.
- What?

475
00:28:07,800 --> 00:28:09,560
For the mechanic to arrive.

476
00:28:09,640 --> 00:28:11,800
Mechanic?
- What's the big deal.

477
00:28:11,880 --> 00:28:13,400
There's a problem with the carburetor.

478
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:15,880
Bablu has called his friend.

479
00:28:15,920 --> 00:28:17,400
Bablu, our driver.

480
00:28:17,480 --> 00:28:19,120
I named him that.

481
00:28:19,840 --> 00:28:22,600
What are we going to do
for one and a half hours?

482
00:28:38,960 --> 00:28:41,000
Great.

483
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:56,400
It's been resolved.

484
00:28:57,360 --> 00:29:00,080
Now.. we travel by
truck to Delhi, is it?

485
00:29:00,160 --> 00:29:01,920
Not all the way to Delhi, but at
least Dharampal will drop us..

486
00:29:01,960 --> 00:29:03,760
..to an inn ahead.

487
00:29:03,840 --> 00:29:05,600
It's the truck driver's name.

488
00:29:06,680 --> 00:29:08,200
I don't know.

489
00:29:08,280 --> 00:29:09,640
I swear that's his name.

490
00:29:09,720 --> 00:29:11,640
I asked him. Dharampal.

491
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:14,760
I don't know whether I
want to go by a truck or not.

492
00:29:14,840 --> 00:29:16,800
I will wait here.

493
00:29:16,880 --> 00:29:19,800
Here? What will you do here
for 11/2 hour in this cold?

494
00:29:19,880 --> 00:29:20,960
And with this fool.

495
00:29:21,040 --> 00:29:22,760
I suggest that you come along.

496
00:29:22,840 --> 00:29:24,440
We will go there and give him a call.

497
00:29:24,520 --> 00:29:26,360
..and tell him where to get the car.

498
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:28,680
And we can have dinner as well.

499
00:29:28,760 --> 00:29:30,080
Come on. Come along.

500
00:29:30,160 --> 00:29:32,560
Come on, madam. Come.

501
00:29:38,760 --> 00:29:42,480
I've left all my luggage in the car.
You think it'll be safe there?

502
00:29:42,560 --> 00:29:44,160
You are getting worried unnecessarily.

503
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:45,920
Your luggage will be absolutely safe.

504
00:29:45,960 --> 00:29:47,720
Three of my bags are there as well.

505
00:29:47,800 --> 00:29:49,320
Bablu will bring them along.

506
00:29:49,400 --> 00:29:51,400
Just relax.
- Right.

507
00:29:53,160 --> 00:29:57,480
First time.. in the truck.
- Yes.

508
00:29:57,560 --> 00:30:01,200
It's quite high.
- High and safe.

509
00:30:01,280 --> 00:30:03,400
Isn't that so, Dharampal?

510
00:30:03,880 --> 00:30:06,960
This vehicle has the pride
of a king, isn't that true?

511
00:30:07,560 --> 00:30:09,720
Rules over the roads

512
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:11,280
There goes a tiny tempo..

513
00:30:11,360 --> 00:30:13,160
And there goes that ant sized scooter

514
00:30:19,720 --> 00:30:21,080
It's been ten minutes.

515
00:30:21,160 --> 00:30:23,120
You are absolutely quiet.

516
00:30:23,440 --> 00:30:25,360
What's wrong?

517
00:30:25,440 --> 00:30:28,840
Are you feeling shy of
the beautiful madam?

518
00:30:29,360 --> 00:30:32,960
No, no, it's not that.
- then what is it?

519
00:30:33,040 --> 00:30:34,560
Why don't you tell a
story of one of your journeys

520
00:30:34,640 --> 00:30:37,200
Like the.. Modi's crazy companion.

521
00:30:37,280 --> 00:30:39,720
It was a show on the radio.

522
00:30:39,800 --> 00:30:41,480
What did it come on?

523
00:30:41,920 --> 00:30:43,960
Radio.
- Yes.

524
00:30:44,920 --> 00:30:46,000
What story should I tell you, sir?

525
00:30:46,080 --> 00:30:48,240
Tell me anything. A story
will make the time fly by.

526
00:30:48,320 --> 00:30:51,360
Once I was driving on
the UP-Patna highway.

527
00:30:51,400 --> 00:30:55,120
And a diesel tanker was lying
toppled in the middle of the highway..

528
00:30:55,200 --> 00:30:56,720
..after ramming into a buffalo.

529
00:30:56,800 --> 00:30:59,160
My truck crushed him.

530
00:30:59,240 --> 00:31:03,360
And his neck came
under my truck's tires.

531
00:31:03,440 --> 00:31:06,760
You mean the entire head.
- Oh, no, the head was gone.

532
00:31:06,800 --> 00:31:09,760
Both his horns sank in his body.

533
00:31:09,840 --> 00:31:11,640
And there were streams of blood.

534
00:31:11,720 --> 00:31:14,040
Just like that.

535
00:31:15,120 --> 00:31:17,040
He died on the spot.

536
00:31:17,480 --> 00:31:19,240
The veins in the neck
must have been severed.

537
00:31:19,320 --> 00:31:24,640
I don't know. - Once I saw an
ovine being slaughtered like that.

538
00:31:24,720 --> 00:31:27,040
You do know what an
ovine is, don't you? Sheep.

539
00:31:27,120 --> 00:31:29,480
Actually the butcher's
knife wasn't sharp enough.

540
00:31:29,560 --> 00:31:30,840
He gave a single blow.

541
00:31:30,920 --> 00:31:34,360
And his head hung like this.

542
00:31:40,840 --> 00:31:43,800
It's okay, you can throw it out.

543
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:45,480
You think so.

544
00:31:50,320 --> 00:31:52,120
How much?

545
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:55,400
Let it be, madam.

546
00:31:55,480 --> 00:31:57,480
Why are you embarrassing me?

547
00:31:58,560 --> 00:32:01,160
My wife is pregnant.

548
00:32:01,240 --> 00:32:04,480
Just pray that everything goes well.

549
00:32:04,560 --> 00:32:06,960
You are giving such big news now.

550
00:32:07,360 --> 00:32:08,960
Sly guy.

551
00:32:09,640 --> 00:32:11,120
I..

552
00:32:12,440 --> 00:32:13,960
Let's..
- Dharampal.

553
00:32:14,000 --> 00:32:17,440
Yes. - Do you always listen
to English songs on the radio?

554
00:32:17,520 --> 00:32:19,160
No, madam.

555
00:32:19,240 --> 00:32:22,080
I played it for you.
- For me?

556
00:32:22,160 --> 00:32:25,960
Yes. I thought you must
listen to English songs.

557
00:32:26,040 --> 00:32:28,840
And she thought you listen to them.

558
00:32:28,920 --> 00:32:30,400
Okay, God bless you.

559
00:32:30,480 --> 00:32:32,080
Call me and tell me what happened.

560
00:32:32,160 --> 00:32:35,120
If it's a girl I'll distribute sweets.

561
00:32:36,800 --> 00:32:38,360
Come on, jump.

562
00:32:38,440 --> 00:32:40,680
You must have never jumped
from a truck before today.

563
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:44,440
All the best. - Thank you.
- Okay, Dharampal, I will call you.

564
00:32:44,520 --> 00:32:45,720
That's so sweet.

565
00:32:45,800 --> 00:32:47,000
And I was wondering..

566
00:32:47,080 --> 00:32:49,600
..since when did truck drivers
start listening to English music?

567
00:32:49,680 --> 00:32:51,440
Careful.

568
00:32:52,200 --> 00:32:54,680
Are you okay?
- Ya.

569
00:32:55,400 --> 00:32:58,560
You're wearing very high heels.

570
00:32:58,880 --> 00:33:00,040
I was wondering..

571
00:33:00,080 --> 00:33:02,520
..why do women wear such high heels?

572
00:33:02,600 --> 00:33:05,640
But these heels are not
meant for walking on these roads.

573
00:33:05,800 --> 00:33:08,160
Don't mistake this road to
be an ordinary one, madam.

574
00:33:08,240 --> 00:33:09,800
I have heard that people
come here in their Mercedes..

575
00:33:09,880 --> 00:33:12,160
..to eat at this inn. Potatoes
with ladyfinger, potatoes with cumin..

576
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:13,280
..potatoes with egg plant, potatoes
with fenugreek, potatoes with..

577
00:33:13,360 --> 00:33:14,640
..cauliflower, peas
and cottage cheese and..

578
00:33:14,720 --> 00:33:16,040
..they even have cold drinks.

579
00:33:16,120 --> 00:33:17,960
So, madam, what will you have?

580
00:33:18,040 --> 00:33:21,200
Anything.
- Anything?

581
00:33:21,280 --> 00:33:23,800
"Anything" isn't
available in this menu.

582
00:33:24,400 --> 00:33:25,840
You will have something.

583
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:31,000
Anything will do as
long as its not very oily.

584
00:33:31,080 --> 00:33:33,480
Which I guess is asking
for too much in this place.

585
00:33:33,560 --> 00:33:35,640
Lets see..

586
00:33:35,720 --> 00:33:39,320
Son. Yes. Come here quickly.

587
00:33:40,920 --> 00:33:42,600
Oh, thank you.
- Great.

588
00:33:42,680 --> 00:33:43,760
He brought a blanket for us.

589
00:33:43,840 --> 00:33:45,600
What is your name?
- Sunny.

590
00:33:45,680 --> 00:33:47,240
Sunny.

591
00:33:47,320 --> 00:33:48,720
Great, Sunny.

592
00:33:48,800 --> 00:33:52,040
Do one thing. Do you eat non-veg?
- No, I don't.

593
00:33:52,120 --> 00:33:53,880
Oh no! Do one thing.

594
00:33:53,960 --> 00:33:57,080
We'll have two plates of Dal,
Two plates of potato with cumin,

595
00:33:57,160 --> 00:33:58,160
Two plates of chick pea curry

596
00:33:58,240 --> 00:33:59,520
two plates of yoghurt salad

597
00:33:59,560 --> 00:34:01,080
And four flatbreads to start with.

598
00:34:01,160 --> 00:34:03,040
Smear the breads with lots of butter.

599
00:34:03,120 --> 00:34:04,760
No, do one thing. Butter two nicely,

600
00:34:04,840 --> 00:34:07,040
And just put a dollop of
butter on the other two. Got it?

601
00:34:07,600 --> 00:34:10,240
That's too much. - But I am so
hungry I could eat an elephant!

602
00:34:10,880 --> 00:34:13,360
And listen. Sunny, right?

603
00:34:14,560 --> 00:34:15,840
Do you see the lady?

604
00:34:15,880 --> 00:34:17,720
She is from Mumbai.

605
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:20,360
She works in movies, she's an actress.

606
00:34:20,440 --> 00:34:22,880
You must have seen her on television,
haven't you?

607
00:34:22,960 --> 00:34:24,600
If she's pleased with your service..

608
00:34:24,680 --> 00:34:26,280
..she will take you to Mumbai.

609
00:34:26,360 --> 00:34:29,800
And cast you as a hero in her
upcoming film "sky full of stars"

610
00:34:29,880 --> 00:34:32,040
In which film?
- She'll cast me as a hero?

611
00:34:32,120 --> 00:34:34,720
What hero? I'm
saying "sky full of stars"

612
00:34:34,800 --> 00:34:36,480
Go, get the food. Yes.

613
00:34:36,560 --> 00:34:38,240
Go quickly.

614
00:34:39,520 --> 00:34:40,760
What was that stupidity?

615
00:34:40,840 --> 00:34:42,800
You wont understand.

616
00:34:42,880 --> 00:34:44,720
Just watch how well they serve us now.

617
00:34:44,800 --> 00:34:45,880
By God!

618
00:34:45,960 --> 00:34:48,080
Next time you want good service..

619
00:34:48,160 --> 00:34:50,200
..don't use my name, okay?

620
00:34:50,280 --> 00:34:51,960
What's the big deal.

621
00:34:52,040 --> 00:34:55,360
Son, turn the fan this way.
- Fan?

622
00:34:56,320 --> 00:34:58,920
Let it be, it's cold.

623
00:35:05,800 --> 00:35:07,760
Wow.

624
00:35:16,120 --> 00:35:18,200
It's delicious.

625
00:35:18,280 --> 00:35:19,640
What are you doing?

626
00:35:19,720 --> 00:35:21,320
Wiping the bread.

627
00:35:21,400 --> 00:35:23,640
You must have an oil-remover cream.

628
00:35:23,720 --> 00:35:25,360
Apply that on the bread.

629
00:35:28,880 --> 00:35:30,760
It's great, just great.

630
00:35:32,880 --> 00:35:35,520
How is the food?
- It's okay.

631
00:35:38,520 --> 00:35:40,240
Thank God.

632
00:35:40,320 --> 00:35:41,480
You didn't taste the Chick pea curry.

633
00:35:41,560 --> 00:35:42,680
It's too oily.

634
00:35:42,760 --> 00:35:44,960
It's locally made butter.

635
00:35:45,040 --> 00:35:46,120
It's very good for health.

636
00:35:46,160 --> 00:35:48,280
Try some.

637
00:35:48,360 --> 00:35:50,640
Eat it.
- Why did you serve it on my plate?

638
00:35:50,720 --> 00:35:53,120
I hate people touching my plate.

639
00:35:53,200 --> 00:35:54,520
Fine, don't eat it.

640
00:35:54,600 --> 00:35:56,120
No one's forcing you.

641
00:35:56,200 --> 00:35:58,200
What's the big deal

642
00:35:59,480 --> 00:36:01,520
Great.

643
00:36:02,960 --> 00:36:06,880
Great. That was delicious.

644
00:36:13,680 --> 00:36:15,360
Why are you laughing?

645
00:36:15,440 --> 00:36:17,680
Go get water, chilled water.

646
00:36:34,640 --> 00:36:36,360
What happened?

647
00:36:37,240 --> 00:36:38,520
My God.

648
00:36:38,600 --> 00:36:40,280
Looks like armpit hair

649
00:36:40,360 --> 00:36:43,000
I can't do this anymore.
- It's okay.

650
00:36:43,080 --> 00:36:45,480
It's clean now after all the steaming
and boiling it's gone through.

651
00:36:45,560 --> 00:36:47,840
Don't worry, just relax and eat.

652
00:36:50,240 --> 00:36:51,800
Please call that driver.

653
00:36:51,880 --> 00:36:54,120
Bablu.
- Yes.

654
00:36:57,640 --> 00:36:59,800
He must have fallen asleep by now.

655
00:37:00,400 --> 00:37:02,360
Give it to me.

656
00:37:06,600 --> 00:37:08,880
Shankar, see if there's a snake.

657
00:37:08,960 --> 00:37:10,680
Snake.

658
00:37:11,320 --> 00:37:13,480
Cockroach.

659
00:37:15,040 --> 00:37:16,320
Cockroach.

660
00:37:16,360 --> 00:37:18,200
Just a minute.

661
00:37:19,520 --> 00:37:22,120
There you go. It's dead.

662
00:37:22,160 --> 00:37:23,400
Stop laughing everyone.

663
00:37:23,480 --> 00:37:25,160
Madam is scared of cockroaches.

664
00:37:25,240 --> 00:37:27,280
I am not used to all this.

665
00:37:27,520 --> 00:37:29,080
And cockroaches are the worst things.

666
00:37:29,160 --> 00:37:31,720
Shut up, enough of laughing.

667
00:37:33,000 --> 00:37:34,760
You call him.

668
00:37:39,920 --> 00:37:41,560
Your phone?

669
00:37:42,240 --> 00:37:45,160
I gave it to you just now.
- Yes.

670
00:37:48,520 --> 00:37:49,960
It must be right here.

671
00:37:50,000 --> 00:37:51,880
Where did it go?

672
00:38:08,520 --> 00:38:10,440
I am really very sorry.

673
00:38:10,520 --> 00:38:13,720
I didn't realize how this
phone slipped from my hand and..

674
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:16,080
That's okay, it keeps falling.

675
00:38:16,160 --> 00:38:18,360
It's still within the warranty.

676
00:38:18,440 --> 00:38:20,280
Will it get repaired? I will get
it repaired once I reach Delhi.

677
00:38:20,360 --> 00:38:22,600
Once it fell in the commode.

678
00:38:22,640 --> 00:38:24,040
I thought it's gone for good.

679
00:38:24,120 --> 00:38:26,440
But those people fixed it in two days.

680
00:38:27,680 --> 00:38:30,400
How will we call the driver now?

681
00:38:30,480 --> 00:38:34,880
I was thinking about the same thing.

682
00:38:34,960 --> 00:38:36,200
Jhujhar Singh.
- Yes.

683
00:38:36,280 --> 00:38:38,440
Can we find any transportation here?
Some scooter or anything.

684
00:38:38,520 --> 00:38:41,640
We don't have a scooter,
but there is a bicycle.

685
00:38:41,800 --> 00:38:42,880
Bicycle. Even that will do.

686
00:38:42,960 --> 00:38:44,040
Should I ask him to fetch it?
- Yes.

687
00:38:44,120 --> 00:38:45,400
Go, get the bicycle quickly.

688
00:38:45,480 --> 00:38:47,520
Get it quickly.

689
00:38:47,560 --> 00:38:49,320
Should I come along?

690
00:38:49,400 --> 00:38:51,880
Where will you go? You sit
here comfortably and relax.

691
00:38:51,960 --> 00:38:53,800
I will go find out.

692
00:38:58,880 --> 00:39:02,440
Is it working?
- No, there is no sound.

693
00:39:02,520 --> 00:39:03,560
Uncle.
- Yes.

694
00:39:03,640 --> 00:39:05,400
Should I go along as well?
- Go on, son.

695
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:09,560
Come, come, climb on. Very good.

696
00:39:09,640 --> 00:39:11,400
Don't you know how
to sit on a bicycle?

697
00:39:11,480 --> 00:39:13,440
Yes, that's correct. Bravo.

698
00:39:15,520 --> 00:39:18,480
Tell me.. why don't you go to school?

699
00:39:19,240 --> 00:39:21,360
Do you want to clean
utensils all your life?

700
00:39:21,440 --> 00:39:23,320
Tell your uncle to get
you out of this inn..

701
00:39:23,400 --> 00:39:25,320
..and send you to school.

702
00:39:25,400 --> 00:39:27,920
Send you where?
- To a school.

703
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:31,520
You're a smart kid.

704
00:39:31,600 --> 00:39:34,560
"Mr. Sharma does long term planning."

705
00:39:34,600 --> 00:39:38,520
"Mr. Verma does not
think of too far ahead."

706
00:39:38,600 --> 00:39:43,320
"So what do you think,
who do you want to be?"

707
00:39:43,400 --> 00:39:45,240
"Invest in smart savings
plan and secure your future."

708
00:39:49,280 --> 00:39:51,280
"Be a Mr. Sharma."

709
00:39:56,560 --> 00:40:00,640
It's bad manners.. to
stare at someone like that.

710
00:40:01,000 --> 00:40:03,840
Shankar, you were going
to the loo, weren't you?

711
00:40:03,920 --> 00:40:06,240
Go on. Go inside.

712
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:28,920
What was that sound?
- It's the wolf.

713
00:40:28,960 --> 00:40:30,240
Wolf?
- Yes.

714
00:40:30,280 --> 00:40:33,400
Wolf. Like a real wolf.
- Yes.

715
00:40:33,960 --> 00:40:35,400
There's a jungle around.

716
00:40:35,480 --> 00:40:37,800
They wander around.

717
00:40:39,000 --> 00:40:41,760
Aren't.. aren't you scared?

718
00:40:42,280 --> 00:40:44,600
There is nothing to be
worried about, madam.

719
00:40:45,240 --> 00:40:48,360
They don't come up
unnecessarily like the snakes.

720
00:40:48,440 --> 00:40:51,240
Snakes?
- Yes, snakes do come here.

721
00:40:51,320 --> 00:40:53,520
And they come in large
numbers in the monsoons.

722
00:40:53,600 --> 00:40:55,240
I saw one just the other day.

723
00:40:55,320 --> 00:40:57,760
It was this long. it passed from here.

724
00:40:57,840 --> 00:41:00,360
But those innocent
creatures don't hurt us.

725
00:41:00,440 --> 00:41:03,640
Instead, they eat up
the mice in our inn.

726
00:41:04,400 --> 00:41:07,000
How was the food madam?

727
00:41:07,080 --> 00:41:09,040
Stop, stop.

728
00:41:10,000 --> 00:41:13,000
I must have lost
10 kilos of weight. I swear.

729
00:41:13,720 --> 00:41:15,200
Jhujhar Singh.

730
00:41:15,280 --> 00:41:17,120
Make some tea.

731
00:41:20,400 --> 00:41:22,600
Where is the car?
- What?

732
00:41:22,680 --> 00:41:25,280
The car?
- The car was towed away.

733
00:41:25,360 --> 00:41:26,760
There was a leakage
in its fuel injection.

734
00:41:26,840 --> 00:41:30,240
So they towed it away.
- Now?

735
00:41:30,320 --> 00:41:32,680
Now what? We will hire another ride.

736
00:41:32,720 --> 00:41:35,760
But.. how can they do that?

737
00:41:35,840 --> 00:41:37,440
They should've sent another car.

738
00:41:37,480 --> 00:41:39,960
That's right. But this is India.

739
00:41:40,080 --> 00:41:42,400
You will have to go to
Delhi and lodge a complaint.

740
00:41:42,480 --> 00:41:45,080
That's why I brought our luggage back.

741
00:41:48,880 --> 00:41:51,080
Where is my bag?
- What?

742
00:41:51,160 --> 00:41:54,920
My bag.
- Which bag?

743
00:41:55,520 --> 00:41:58,160
My black suitcase.

744
00:42:01,880 --> 00:42:03,760
Oh! That's what I kept
wondering on the way..

745
00:42:03,840 --> 00:42:05,320
..what have I missed..

746
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:06,960
What?

747
00:42:07,480 --> 00:42:09,760
You left my bag in the car.

748
00:42:09,840 --> 00:42:11,960
What's the big deal, we
still have the receipt.

749
00:42:12,040 --> 00:42:15,480
We'll call the car-owners and
they will deliver the luggage.

750
00:42:15,560 --> 00:42:17,600
Receipt?

751
00:42:17,680 --> 00:42:19,760
It was in the car.
- Really?

752
00:42:19,840 --> 00:42:21,280
Did you take it?

753
00:42:21,360 --> 00:42:25,480
But we do know.. the
name of the driver. - Bablu.

754
00:42:25,560 --> 00:42:27,760
Yes.
- Wow.

755
00:42:28,640 --> 00:42:30,960
What will I do with that name?

756
00:42:31,080 --> 00:42:33,720
All my belongings were in that bag.

757
00:42:33,800 --> 00:42:38,520
My clothes, my files, everything.

758
00:42:39,880 --> 00:42:41,520
How can you do this?

759
00:42:41,600 --> 00:42:43,520
You have only lost your belongings.

760
00:42:43,600 --> 00:42:44,920
So what.

761
00:42:45,000 --> 00:42:46,680
Things like these happen sometimes.

762
00:42:46,760 --> 00:42:48,800
You shouldn't let it
bother you so much.

763
00:42:48,880 --> 00:42:50,120
Because I believe
that the only thing..

764
00:42:50,200 --> 00:42:52,240
.. that matters in life,
is life itself!

765
00:42:54,960 --> 00:42:56,680
And we're still alive.

766
00:42:56,760 --> 00:42:58,520
You are rinsing your mouth..

767
00:42:58,600 --> 00:43:00,960
..with my French Alps Spring water?

768
00:43:01,840 --> 00:43:03,400
So what's the big deal.

769
00:43:03,480 --> 00:43:05,280
You're arguing with me
for a bottle of water.

770
00:43:05,360 --> 00:43:07,440
I will buy you
another one. Jhujhar Singh.

771
00:43:07,520 --> 00:43:10,080
Give madam two
litres of mineral water.

772
00:43:10,160 --> 00:43:12,280
What's the big deal.
- What's the big deal!

773
00:43:12,360 --> 00:43:13,800
What's the big deal!

774
00:43:13,880 --> 00:43:15,960
What is a big deal for you?

775
00:43:16,080 --> 00:43:19,640
When wolves come in and
attack us and eat us..

776
00:43:19,720 --> 00:43:21,280
..that will be a big deal for you.

777
00:43:21,360 --> 00:43:22,440
And you, madam.

778
00:43:22,520 --> 00:43:24,800
Everything is bad news for you.

779
00:43:24,880 --> 00:43:28,680
Even your good starts
with not too bad, you know.

780
00:43:28,760 --> 00:43:30,760
That's it, I have had it.

781
00:43:30,800 --> 00:43:34,040
You are the worst person
I have ever met. - Really?

782
00:43:34,120 --> 00:43:35,920
