You don't have any sense. Let's go.

1544
01:30:16,060 --> 01:30:17,380
This is my husband.

1545
01:30:17,460 --> 01:30:19,300
Lt. Colonel Vikram Singh Rana.

1546
01:30:19,380 --> 01:30:21,820
And he is the one who brought me here.

1547
01:30:21,980 --> 01:30:25,540
Hello.
- Not him. Him.

1548
01:30:25,700 --> 01:30:27,140
Hello.

1549
01:30:27,540 --> 01:30:29,060
'Hail the youth, hail the farmers.'

1550
01:30:29,140 --> 01:30:31,300
Don't fight amongst yourselves,
understand?

1551
01:30:31,380 --> 01:30:32,900
Let's go, the riots are over. Come.

1552
01:30:32,980 --> 01:30:34,620
Mr. Pandey, Mr. Bhaiyya.. it's okay.

1553
01:30:34,700 --> 01:30:38,060
And you know, he fed the
TC Ghevar (a sweet snack).

1554
01:30:38,140 --> 01:30:40,820
Hey, you don't know, he was
asking for Gulabjamun (a sweetmeat).

1555
01:30:46,700 --> 01:30:49,380
You went through all that.

1556
01:30:49,980 --> 01:30:52,060
Oh, God.
- That was great, nice meeting you.

1557
01:30:52,140 --> 01:30:54,380
Thank you, nice meeting you too.
- Well done, well done.

1558
01:30:54,700 --> 01:30:56,380
Let me tell you one thing.
I wonder what would have happened..

1559
01:30:56,460 --> 01:30:57,700
..to my wife if it wasn't for you.

1560
01:30:57,820 --> 01:30:58,700
What would have happened?

1561
01:30:58,740 --> 01:31:00,900
I would have reached
Delhi on time yesterday.

1562
01:31:00,980 --> 01:31:03,220
Isn't that right?
- You are just..

1563
01:31:04,220 --> 01:31:05,540
Later.

1564
01:31:07,060 --> 01:31:09,300
Well, at least call home now.

1565
01:31:09,380 --> 01:31:10,980
They must be so worried.

1566
01:31:11,540 --> 01:31:12,620
There is no need for that.

1567
01:31:12,700 --> 01:31:14,140
We are almost home.

1568
01:31:14,380 --> 01:31:15,620
What kind of a person are you?

1569
01:31:15,620 --> 01:31:17,220
Such an ego. And that too, male ego.

1570
01:31:17,300 --> 01:31:19,220
It's just not done.
- It's not like that..

1571
01:31:19,300 --> 01:31:21,820
She is right. Why
don't you just call home.

1572
01:31:21,900 --> 01:31:23,820
I insist. Give him the phone.

1573
01:31:28,060 --> 01:31:29,620
What happened?
- My phone.

1574
01:31:29,980 --> 01:31:31,380
I can't find my phone.

1575
01:31:31,540 --> 01:31:34,300
Did you leave it back at the hotel?

1576
01:31:34,540 --> 01:31:35,740
Yes, that's right.

1577
01:31:35,820 --> 01:31:39,060
Should I take a u-turn?
- No big deal.

1578
01:31:40,140 --> 01:31:41,900
That's a nice attitude.

1579
01:31:42,380 --> 01:31:44,700
You have developed a great attitude.

1580
01:31:45,740 --> 01:31:48,620
Here.
- No, no, really..

1581
01:31:48,700 --> 01:31:49,820
Call her, that's okay.

1582
01:31:49,900 --> 01:31:53,060
I insist, call her.
- Okay, if you insist.

1583
01:31:57,460 --> 01:31:58,540
Hello.

1584
01:31:58,700 --> 01:31:59,900
Yes, it's me.

1585
01:32:00,140 --> 01:32:03,980
The flight was diverted
from Delhi to Jaipur..

1586
01:32:04,060 --> 01:32:05,620
You won't understand.

1587
01:32:05,820 --> 01:32:07,300
I am coming.

1588
01:32:07,740 --> 01:32:09,820
I am not making any excuses.

1589
01:32:09,900 --> 01:32:11,380
You are just.. Listen.

1590
01:32:11,460 --> 01:32:12,620
This is not my phone.

1591
01:32:12,700 --> 01:32:13,820
I can't talk to you for too long.

1592
01:32:13,900 --> 01:32:15,460
That's okay, you can talk to her.
- That's okay. - Yes.

1593
01:32:15,540 --> 01:32:17,540
No, no, I am almost there.
I will come see you.

1594
01:32:17,620 --> 01:32:20,820
You don't know, once Vibha starts,
she doesn't stop.

1595
01:32:21,380 --> 01:32:22,620
Thank you.

1596
01:32:26,900 --> 01:32:28,620
Stop on the left.

1597
01:32:28,700 --> 01:32:30,820
Your home is here.
- No, it's in the alley inside.

1598
01:32:30,900 --> 01:32:32,540
Then I will take it inside.
- No, no..

1599
01:32:32,620 --> 01:32:34,820
The car won't go inside.
I will walk on foot.

1600
01:32:34,900 --> 01:32:36,700
By God, let it be. I mean it.

1601
01:32:36,740 --> 01:32:38,820
It's very far inside.

1602
01:32:38,900 --> 01:32:40,980
Very far for you, but near for me.

1603
01:32:41,460 --> 01:32:43,380
Sure?
- Yes. 100 percent.

1604
01:32:43,460 --> 01:32:45,540
Shall I stop here?
- Yes.

1605
01:32:46,060 --> 01:32:50,380
Go ahead and take right. That's it.

1606
01:32:51,460 --> 01:32:52,700
Stop here, here.

1607
01:32:53,220 --> 01:32:55,060
Okay.
- We've reached Delhi, thank you.

1608
01:32:55,140 --> 01:32:57,900
Nice meeting you.
- Thanks, sir. Salutations, sir.

1609
01:32:58,380 --> 01:32:59,460
Okay.

1610
01:33:02,460 --> 01:33:03,700
I..

1611
01:33:06,380 --> 01:33:09,060
Okay, colonel. See you.
- Look after yourself.

1612
01:33:09,140 --> 01:33:10,540
Thanks for the lift.

1613
01:33:15,300 --> 01:33:17,460
Why is she getting down?
What happened?

1614
01:33:19,980 --> 01:33:21,620
So I guess this is it.

1615
01:33:21,700 --> 01:33:24,300
Yes, this is my Chandni Chowk.

1616
01:33:25,620 --> 01:33:30,380
No, I mean.. the end of our journey.

1617
01:33:30,460 --> 01:33:32,980
Yes, the journey has ended.

1618
01:33:33,060 --> 01:33:35,460
We have reached Delhi. Who knew..
- Yes.

1619
01:33:36,380 --> 01:33:38,820
I was saying..

1620
01:33:39,540 --> 01:33:43,740
..I apologize for any..

1621
01:33:43,820 --> 01:33:45,380
No, please.

1622
01:33:46,220 --> 01:33:50,540
Whatever it was I have to say..
it was very interesting.

1623
01:33:50,620 --> 01:33:52,140
Mr..

1624
01:33:54,900 --> 01:33:56,140
Brother.

1625
01:33:56,460 --> 01:33:59,140
I think you didn't
read my name on the card.

1626
01:33:59,620 --> 01:34:02,620
It's okay. My name is Manu Gupta.

1627
01:34:05,300 --> 01:34:06,820
Mihika Banerjee.

1628
01:34:08,540 --> 01:34:10,140
Nice to meet you.

1629
01:34:11,060 --> 01:34:12,300
Very nice to meet you.

1630
01:34:12,540 --> 01:34:13,820
Goodbye.

1631
01:34:37,740 --> 01:34:40,220
Oh! I am so tired.

1632
01:34:45,220 --> 01:34:46,620
What is that?

1633
01:34:47,700 --> 01:34:51,700
Flowers of henna are soaked in vinegar

1634
01:34:51,820 --> 01:34:54,380
and then mixed with elephants poop..

1635
01:34:54,460 --> 01:34:57,140
Headache formula.
- Are you serious?

1636
01:34:57,220 --> 01:35:01,620
Yes, A-one formula for
Head aches and body aches.

1637
01:35:01,700 --> 01:35:03,060
It belongs to him.

1638
01:35:03,300 --> 01:35:05,820
And I am going to use it.
- Please use it.

1639
01:35:05,900 --> 01:35:07,380
Oh, no.

1640
01:35:07,820 --> 01:35:11,380
Listen, your ad office had called.

1641
01:35:11,820 --> 01:35:14,740
Oh, no, I forgot to call them.

1642
01:35:15,220 --> 01:35:16,300
Vikram, where is your phone?

1643
01:35:16,380 --> 01:35:18,220
There it is.
- That's it.

1644
01:35:24,220 --> 01:35:25,460
Hi, Vineet.

1645
01:35:25,620 --> 01:35:27,740
Sorry, I couldn't call you back.

1646
01:35:28,220 --> 01:35:29,980
No, I was tied up in something.

1647
01:35:30,060 --> 01:35:33,540
Listen, I have figured out
what is missing in that ad.

1648
01:35:33,900 --> 01:35:37,060
Whether it's Mr. Sharma or Mr. Verma,
it doesn't make a difference.

1649
01:35:37,140 --> 01:35:38,820
I think that should be the end.

1650
01:35:39,460 --> 01:35:41,460
Yes, okay.

1651
01:35:41,700 --> 01:35:42,980
And listen.

1652
01:35:43,060 --> 01:35:44,220
I am in Delhi on Monday..

1653
01:35:44,300 --> 01:35:46,620
..so if you want to drop by,
you can come at anytime, okay?

1654
01:35:46,820 --> 01:35:49,140
Okay. Bye.

1655
01:35:51,980 --> 01:35:54,380
You were supposed to
go to the US on Monday.

1656
01:35:54,460 --> 01:35:56,540
What happened?
- I am not going.

1657
01:35:56,740 --> 01:35:58,380
Are you sure?
- Yes.

1658
01:35:58,620 --> 01:36:01,300
Why?
- Because you are going to..

1659
01:36:01,380 --> 01:36:04,140
..throw my birthday party on Sunday.

1660
01:36:04,220 --> 01:36:06,220
And the next day, I will be hung over.

1661
01:36:06,700 --> 01:36:08,140
So I will go after that.

1662
01:36:08,900 --> 01:36:10,380
You have changed.

1663
01:36:14,300 --> 01:36:15,380
Listen..

1664
01:36:15,820 --> 01:36:19,300
Look there in the pocket.

1665
01:36:19,380 --> 01:36:20,980
I brought something for you.

1666
01:36:21,060 --> 01:36:23,820
Take a look, it's in my jacket.
- Really? - Your birthday gift.

1667
01:36:24,140 --> 01:36:25,980
Yes. Found it.

1668
01:36:29,220 --> 01:36:31,220
Oh, my, God. Vikram, it's beautiful,

1669
01:36:32,620 --> 01:36:33,900
You like it?

1670
01:36:41,060 --> 01:36:42,380
I am so lucky.

1671
01:36:42,900 --> 01:36:45,300
I have the most
wonderful husband in the world.

1672
01:36:47,540 --> 01:36:48,540
And I want to celebrate my birthday..

1673
01:36:48,620 --> 01:36:51,700
..with my friends
and family at my home.

1674
01:36:52,460 --> 01:36:55,220
There's still time
before we reach home. - Yes.

1675
01:36:55,300 --> 01:36:57,220
Let's make a list.
- Yes. Great.

1676
01:36:57,300 --> 01:36:59,140
Tell me, who do you want to invite?

1677
01:36:59,220 --> 01:37:00,740
The usual suspects.
- Okay.

1678
01:37:00,820 --> 01:37:02,140
Sangeeta.
- Sangeeta.

1679
01:37:02,220 --> 01:37:04,140
Kunal.
- Kunal. - Jeet. - Jeet.

1680
01:37:04,620 --> 01:37:07,540
Why don't we call him..
Your friend from this journey?

1681
01:37:07,620 --> 01:37:09,140
Why not invite him?

1682
01:37:09,220 --> 01:37:10,900
You have the best ideas.

1683
01:37:13,540 --> 01:37:15,900
Where is my phone?
- Yes.

1684
01:37:16,140 --> 01:37:17,820
It must be the last dialed number..

1685
01:37:17,900 --> 01:37:19,380
Call him back.
- Of course.

1686
01:37:23,460 --> 01:37:27,060
The number you have dialed is invalid.

1687
01:37:27,900 --> 01:37:29,140
What happened?

1688
01:37:29,220 --> 01:37:31,300
They are saying it's
an invalid number.

1689
01:37:31,380 --> 01:37:32,540
Show me.

1690
01:37:34,540 --> 01:37:37,220
You seem to have
dialed a wrong number.

1691
01:37:37,300 --> 01:37:40,060
Please check the number.. - Yes,
its an invalid number you have dialed.

1692
01:37:40,380 --> 01:37:41,900
Why would he do that?

1693
01:37:43,620 --> 01:37:45,140
Why would he?

1694
01:37:48,380 --> 01:37:50,060
Vikram, turn the car around please.

1695
01:37:50,380 --> 01:37:53,060
Are you sure? - Please. - Yes, just..
just turn the car around.

1696
01:38:03,900 --> 01:38:06,900
Where are you going?
- I want to find out something.

1697
01:38:06,980 --> 01:38:08,380
Should I come along?
- No. I am fine.

1698
01:38:08,460 --> 01:38:11,140
Are you sure?
- Yes. - Just two minutes.

1699
01:38:24,900 --> 01:38:28,060
Excuse me, do you know
where Manu Gupta lives?

1700
01:38:28,140 --> 01:38:29,220
I don't know that.

1701
01:38:29,300 --> 01:38:30,700
But please taste these kebabs.

1702
01:38:30,820 --> 01:38:32,380
No, thank you.

1703
01:38:44,380 --> 01:38:46,620
Excuse me, do you
know where Manu Gupta..

1704
01:38:46,700 --> 01:38:49,820
..who has a shop in Karol Baug, lives?

1705
01:38:49,900 --> 01:38:51,460
Mr. Gupta.
- Yes.

1706
01:38:51,540 --> 01:38:53,540
Go into the alley right in front.
- Yes.

1707
01:38:53,540 --> 01:38:56,460
It's the first house on the left.
- Okay.

1708
01:38:56,540 --> 01:38:58,060
Thank you.
- Okay.

1709
01:39:57,820 --> 01:40:00,820
Manu uncle's home.
- Yes.

1710
01:40:00,900 --> 01:40:03,460
It's the last house.
- Okay, thank you.

1711
01:40:18,060 --> 01:40:21,460
Hello, does Manu Gupta stay here?

1712
01:40:21,540 --> 01:40:23,620
Someone's at the door for you.

1713
01:40:25,700 --> 01:40:27,380
Just coming

1714
01:40:30,540 --> 01:40:31,900
Its you!

1715
01:40:34,980 --> 01:40:36,460
Your wife.

1716
01:40:38,980 --> 01:40:40,460
She's still angry?

1717
01:40:40,820 --> 01:40:42,460
No, she wasn't my wife.

1718
01:40:42,900 --> 01:40:44,300
She is the nurse.

1719
01:40:45,540 --> 01:40:46,900
My wife..

1720
01:40:48,980 --> 01:40:51,220
Come in. Come on.

1721
01:40:53,980 --> 01:40:55,220
Come in.

1722
01:40:57,460 --> 01:41:00,820
She is my wife, Vibha.

1723
01:41:11,820 --> 01:41:13,300
Vibha, look who is here.

1724
01:41:13,620 --> 01:41:14,900
Mihika.

1725
01:41:15,300 --> 01:41:17,980
The one I was telling you about.

1726
01:41:19,140 --> 01:41:23,220
Two years ago,
she got high fever and..

1727
01:41:24,140 --> 01:41:25,620
..it went up here.

1728
01:41:30,140 --> 01:41:31,300
To her brain.

1729
01:41:32,460 --> 01:41:34,980
And since then, she is in coma.

1730
01:41:36,740 --> 01:41:37,820
Why..

1731
01:41:38,540 --> 01:41:42,060
Why didn't you tell me?

1732
01:41:43,460 --> 01:41:45,900
I never told anyone anything.

1733
01:41:46,540 --> 01:41:49,540
Why are you standing? Sit down.

1734
01:41:54,220 --> 01:41:56,220
What's the point in telling anyone?

1735
01:41:56,620 --> 01:41:59,460
The more I tell people,
the more they'll sympathize.

1736
01:41:59,540 --> 01:42:02,980
And the more they sympathize,
The more it'll hurt me.

1737
01:42:03,220 --> 01:42:06,460
And I don't want to live like that.

1738
01:42:07,820 --> 01:42:11,540
The truth is that when
something is not in our control..

1739
01:42:11,900 --> 01:42:13,980
..its foolish to let it affect you.

1740
01:42:14,380 --> 01:42:19,980
I believe.. change what you
can and accept what you cant.

1741
01:42:19,980 --> 01:42:23,140
What? I said, accept it.

1742
01:42:24,300 --> 01:42:26,980
But your children.

1743
01:42:27,060 --> 01:42:28,540
I have two daughters.

1744
01:42:28,620 --> 01:42:29,820
Shraddha and Archana.

1745
01:42:29,900 --> 01:42:32,220
They live in Meerut
with my elder sister.

1746
01:42:32,820 --> 01:42:36,820
I stay out of the house
half the time for work.

1747
01:42:37,220 --> 01:42:38,700
So they are better off with her.

1748
01:42:38,740 --> 01:42:40,300
They do come here
sometimes on Sundays.

1749
01:42:41,380 --> 01:42:43,540
This is my family.

1750
01:42:44,620 --> 01:42:46,980
Wife's here, children are there.

1751
01:42:47,300 --> 01:42:50,060
And I, from here to there.

1752
01:42:50,300 --> 01:42:52,140
A wandering traveler,

1753
01:42:52,300 --> 01:42:55,140
And what do the doctors say?

1754
01:42:55,220 --> 01:42:56,820
What would the doctors say?

1755
01:42:59,980 --> 01:43:01,460
The doctors have..

1756
01:43:03,700 --> 01:43:05,820
.. stopped saying anything,
just like her.

1757
01:43:05,900 --> 01:43:07,300
All of them are quiet.

1758
01:43:10,820 --> 01:43:17,220
But I am sure that one day my
Vibha will be cured 100 percent?

1759
01:43:19,140 --> 01:43:20,540
How sure?

1760
01:43:21,620 --> 01:43:23,900
100 percent.

1761
01:43:25,820 --> 01:43:28,140
You are a shameless woman.

1762
01:43:28,380 --> 01:43:29,700
There's a guest at Home who
has come for the first time..

1763
01:43:29,820 --> 01:43:31,300
..and you didn't
even ask her for water.

1764
01:43:31,620 --> 01:43:33,300
She has grown lazy.

1765
01:43:34,140 --> 01:43:35,900
I will get water for you.

1766
01:43:40,820 --> 01:43:42,300
Now I understand..

1767
01:43:44,820 --> 01:43:46,540
What the big deal was.

1768
01:43:49,140 --> 01:43:50,620
What did you say?

1769
01:43:52,220 --> 01:43:53,700
Just that..

1770
01:43:54,540 --> 01:43:58,820
..when something so devastating
has happened in someone's life..

1771
01:43:59,900 --> 01:44:02,980
..then nothing else
seems like a big deal..

1772
01:44:03,220 --> 01:44:04,980
It's just a point of view.

1773
01:44:05,300 --> 01:44:06,540
See..

1774
01:44:07,460 --> 01:44:09,900
No matter in what
condition my wife is in..

1775
01:44:11,140 --> 01:44:12,540
..at least she is with me.

1776
01:44:13,740 --> 01:44:15,060
And you know.

1777
01:44:15,700 --> 01:44:17,820
Vibha isn't an ordinary wife.

1778
01:44:18,220 --> 01:44:20,540
She's the only wife in the world..

1779
01:44:20,820 --> 01:44:22,820
..who doesn't argue with her husband.

1780
01:44:25,820 --> 01:44:27,900
So you too learnt to
laugh at your sorrows.

1781
01:44:28,700 --> 01:44:30,300
Here.
- Thank you.

1782
01:44:33,900 --> 01:44:37,140
But there is one thing
I still didn't quite get..

1783
01:44:38,460 --> 01:44:41,060
Why did you suddenly.. return

1784
01:44:42,820 --> 01:44:45,380
Actually tomorrow, which is a Sunday

1785
01:44:45,460 --> 01:44:47,300
There is a party at my home.

1786
01:44:47,380 --> 01:44:51,620
And Vikram and
I wanted to invite you for it.

1787
01:44:52,460 --> 01:44:57,540
Me? - Look, you tried to
avoid us even earlier.

1788
01:44:57,980 --> 01:45:02,380
But I found your home.
- No, I..

1789
01:45:02,700 --> 01:45:04,460
No excuses this time.

1790
01:45:04,700 --> 01:45:06,220
Do come.

1791
01:45:06,380 --> 01:45:08,300
You do remember the address,
don't you?

1792
01:45:08,380 --> 01:45:11,700
Chanakyapuri, Ninth main,
bungalow no. 44.

1793
01:45:11,820 --> 01:45:13,220
Yes, I do.
- Exactly.

1794
01:45:13,300 --> 01:45:17,060
No, actually you..
It's such a big party.

1795
01:45:17,140 --> 01:45:21,460
And I will look out of
place amongst your friends.

1796
01:45:21,540 --> 01:45:24,820
